	 <tr>
           <td width='110' class='bodyweight-title'>BODY WEIGHT:</td>
	   <td width='80' class='bodyweight-amount'>95 lb</td>
         </tr>
	</table>

<br/><br/>
<!-- End DoseChart  -->
<!-- Start Body -->

ahh, what can i say about adderall?  from someone who has a HIGH tolerance for speed, its better than shards,coke,crystal,and crank.  <BR>
<BR>
it doesnt leave me with that all too familiar feign for just another bump. all of my senses are multiplied by 1000. I take it and about 1 hour later, I have strength like a gladiator, my vision is crystal clear, I truly feel every part of my body working. the complexity & subconscious of my mind is peeping its little petals out like a flower just blooming. <BR>
<BR>
my body feels absolutely tingly like when I was a kid squishing my naked foot in the mud & wiggling it around. a drag off a cigarette tastes heavenly. I sit down pause and realize I can be exactly on the same level & page as everyone. coming from an angel, I truly got a taste of heaven and a whiff of an angel's wings,..hell I bounced on cloud 9.<!-- End Body -->
<br/><br style="clear:both;"/>


